This Market Trend Spotter function is a comprehensive tool for monitoring and analyzing trends in the luxury watch market. It includes:

Data Collection:

Price observations for specific watch models
Auction results tracking
Waitlist/availability information
Market insights and observations


Trend Analysis:

Price trend detection (increasing, decreasing, stable)
Demand trend analysis
Brand performance metrics
Market sentiment assessment


Opportunity Identification:

Rising stars (models with increasing prices and demand)
Undervalued watches (high demand but stable prices)
Potential peaked models (price increases but cooling demand)


Market Intelligence:

Availability insights (hard-to-find models, changing availability)
Auction performance analysis
Brand-level market performance
Overall market sentiment indicators


Reporting:

Comprehensive market reports
Emerging trend alerts
Performance metrics across different timeframes



The function supports three main actions:

add: Add new market data points (prices, auction results, waitlist info)
analyze: Perform trend analysis over a specified period
report: Generate a comprehensive market report

This function serves as the market intelligence component of your Luxury Watch Investment Advisor, helping collectors and investors identify trends and opportunities in the luxury watch market.
